### Update delivery boy location
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/tracking/location
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "latitude": 12.9716,
    "longitude": 77.5946,
    "orderId": "PASTE_ORDER_ID_HERE"
}

### Track order live location
GET http://localhost:8000/api/tracking/order/PASTE_ORDER_ID_HERE

### Get order location history
GET http://localhost:8000/api/tracking/order/PASTE_ORDER_ID_HERE/history

### Get available delivery boys location
GET http://localhost:8000/api/tracking/available-delivery-boys